    "summary": "STAMFORD, CT, May 26, 2026--Regulatory News: Philip Morris International Inc. (PMI) (NYSE: PM) will host a live webcast of the company’s remarks and Q&A session with Jacek Olczak, Group CEO PMI, at the 2026 dbAccess Global Consumer Conference on Tuesday, June 2, 2026, at approximately 11:15 a.m. CET (5:15 a.m. ET). The webcast will be available here, with a post-event recording available for one year at the same site.",
